@* Kimlik doƒürulamasƒ± yapƒ±lmƒ±≈ü kullanƒ±cƒ±lar i√ßin Dashboard sayfasƒ± *@
@model SO.Application.DTOs.Dashboard.DashboardStatisticsDto

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Panel";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="page-header fade-in" style="padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-1">
                    <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt me-2 text-primary"></i>
                    Panel
                </h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
                    @ViewBag.WelcomeMessage - @if (ViewBag.IsAdmin == true) { <text>Y√∂netici g√∂r√ºn√ºm√º - T√ºm sistem verileri</text> } else { <text>Ki≈üisel veri √∂zetiniz</text> }
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-md-end">
                <a asp-controller="Proposals" asp-action="Create" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-plus me-2"></i>Yeni Teklif
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Statistics Cards - Proposal Status -->
    <div class="row g-2 mb-4">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card stat-card-compact bg-gradient-secondary text-white hover-lift">
                <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <div class="stat-icon-compact me-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-content-compact">
                            <h4 class="stat-number-compact mb-0">@(Model?.DraftProposalsCount ?? 0)</h4>
                            <p class="stat-label-compact mb-0">üìã Taslak</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card stat-card-compact bg-gradient-primary text-white hover-lift">
                <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <div class="stat-icon-compact me-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-content-compact">
                            <h4 class="stat-number-compact mb-0">@(Model?.SentProposalsCount ?? 0)</h4>
                            <p class="stat-label-compact mb-0">üì® G√∂nderildi</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card stat-card-compact bg-gradient-success text-white hover-lift">
                <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <div class="stat-icon-compact me-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-content-compact">
                            <h4 class="stat-number-compact mb-0">@(Model?.ApprovedProposalsCount ?? 0)</h4>
                            <p class="stat-label-compact mb-0">‚úÖ Onaylandƒ±</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card stat-card-compact bg-gradient-danger text-white hover-lift">
                <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <div class="stat-icon-compact me-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-content-compact">
                            <h4 class="stat-number-compact mb-0">@(Model?.RejectedProposalsCount ?? 0)</h4>
                            <p class="stat-label-compact mb-0">‚ùå Reddedildi</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card stat-card-compact bg-gradient-warning text-white hover-lift">
                <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <div class="stat-icon-compact me-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-ban"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-content-compact">
                            <h4 class="stat-number-compact mb-0">@(Model?.CancelledProposalsCount ?? 0)</h4>
                            <p class="stat-label-compact mb-0">‚õî ƒ∞ptal Edildi</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Recent Activity & Quick Stats -->
    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h3 class="card-title mb-0">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line me-2 text-success"></i>
                        Son Aktiviteler
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="activity-timeline">
                        @if (Model?.BusinessActivities != null && Model.BusinessActivities.Any())
                        {
                            <!-- ƒ∞lk 3 aktiviteyi g√∂ster -->
                            <div id="initialActivities">
                                @foreach (var activity in Model.BusinessActivities.Take(3))
                                {
                                    <div class="activity-item d-flex align-items-start mb-4">
                                        <div class="activity-icon me-3">
                                            <div class="icon-circle @activity.IconColor text-white">
                                                <i class="@activity.IconClass"></i>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="activity-content">
                                            <h6 class="activity-title mb-1">@activity.Title</h6>
                                            <p class="activity-description text-muted mb-1">@activity.Description</p>
                                            <small class="text-muted">@activity.TimeAgo</small>
                                            @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(activity.ActivityType) && activity.ActivityType != "System")
                                            {
                                                <br/>
                                                <small class="text-info">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-tag me-1"></i>@activity.ActivityType
                                                    @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(activity.Status))
                                                    {
                                                        <span class="ms-2">| <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-1"></i>@activity.Status</span>
                                                    }
                                                    @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(activity.UserName))
                                                    {
                                                        <span class="ms-2">| <i class="fas fa-user me-1"></i>@activity.UserName</span>
                                                    }
                                                </small>
                                            }
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                }
                            </div>

                            <!-- Gizli aktiviteler -->
                            @if (Model.BusinessActivities.Count > 3)
                            {
                                <div id="hiddenActivities" style="display: none;">
                                    @foreach (var activity in Model.BusinessActivities.Skip(3))
                                    {
                                        <div class="activity-item d-flex align-items-start mb-4">
                                            <div class="activity-icon me-3">
                                                <div class="icon-circle @activity.IconColor text-white">
                                                    <i class="@activity.IconClass"></i>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="activity-content">
                                                <h6 class="activity-title mb-1">@activity.Title</h6>
                                                <p class="activity-description text-muted mb-1">@activity.Description</p>
                                                <small class="text-muted">@activity.TimeAgo</small>
                                                @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(activity.ActivityType) && activity.ActivityType != "System")
                                                {
                                                    <br/>
                                                    <small class="text-info">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-tag me-1"></i>@activity.ActivityType
                                                        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(activity.Status))
                                                        {
                                                            <span class="ms-2">| <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-1"></i>@activity.Status</span>
                                                        }
                                                        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(activity.UserName))
                                                        {
                                                            <span class="ms-2">| <i class="fas fa-user me-1"></i>@activity.UserName</span>
                                                        }
                                                    </small>
                                                }
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    }
                                </div>

                                <!-- Daha fazla g√∂ster butonu -->
                                <div class="text-center mt-3">
                                    <button class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm" id="showMoreBtn" onclick="toggleActivities()">
                                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down me-1"></i>Daha fazla g√∂ster (@(Model.BusinessActivities.Count - 3) aktivite)
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            }
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <div class="text-center py-4">
                                <i class="fas fa-info-circle text-muted mb-3" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
                                <p class="text-muted mb-0">√áalƒ±≈ümaya ba≈ülayƒ±n ve son aktivitelerinizi burada g√∂r√ºn</p>
                            </div>
                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h3 class="card-title mb-0">
                        <i class="fas fa-tasks me-2 text-warning"></i>
                        Performans √ñzeti
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="quick-stats">
                        <div class="stat-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3 pb-3 border-bottom">
                            <span class="stat-label">üìã Taslak</span>
                            <span class="stat-value text-secondary fw-bold">@(Model?.DraftProposalsCount ?? 0)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3 pb-3 border-bottom">
                            <span class="stat-label">üì® G√∂nderildi</span>
                            <span class="stat-value text-primary fw-bold">@(Model?.SentProposalsCount ?? 0)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3 pb-3 border-bottom">
                            <span class="stat-label">‚úÖ Onaylandƒ±</span>
                            <span class="stat-value text-success fw-bold">@(Model?.ApprovedProposalsCount ?? 0)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3 pb-3 border-bottom">
                            <span class="stat-label">‚ùå Reddedildi</span>
                            <span class="stat-value text-danger fw-bold">@(Model?.RejectedProposalsCount ?? 0)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <span class="stat-label">‚õî ƒ∞ptal Edildi</span>
                            <span class="stat-value text-warning fw-bold">@(Model?.CancelledProposalsCount ?? 0)</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Styles {
    <style>
        /* Soft Gradient Colors */
        .bg-gradient-secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #95a5b8 0%, #b8c5d6 100%) !important;
        }
        
        .bg-gradient-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6ba3f5 0%, #8fc0ff 100%) !important;
        }
        
        .bg-gradient-success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5fb894 0%, #88d9b8 100%) !important;
        }
        
        .bg-gradient-danger {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f08a8a 0%, #ffb0b0 100%) !important;
        }
        
        .bg-gradient-warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc168 0%, #ffd699 100%) !important;
        }
        
        /* Compact Stat Cards */
